{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aaa1b91015","title":"给向偶的信叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a21d612b83","index":0,"year":1939,"month":9,"day":5,"articleId":"aaa1b91015"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji13","name":"毛泽东全集第13卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji13.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji13":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c3fd4d7c6e","type":"paragraph","text":"给向偶的信叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"aaa1b91015"},{"id":"3ddff63a2a","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年9月5日）取名延生如何？如以为不妥，请你们自己拟出两三个，我替你们选择一个。因忙退复，是以为款！此复向、唐二同志并庆视你们的小孩。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"aaa1b91015"},{"id":"2670182a6a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"aaa1b91015"},{"id":"48e65277df","type":"paragraph","text":"九月五日[1]1939年7月1日，音乐家向属、唐荣妆的第二个儿子降生在延安的密利里，他们想请毛泽东给孩子取个名字，但考虚到毛泽东那么忙，难以房齿。8月18日，孩子的费桐蓝，当时是普迅文学院的学生，知道这件事后，自告奋男，从练习本上撕下一页纸，给毛泽东写了一封信。信是这样写的：“我们的小孩-—一个男孩一是七月一日生下来的，因为他刚巧在伟大的日子里进入了这伟大的时代，我们都希得到你的光荣给他取一个名字.研究院向隔同志收”。打开一看，毛泽东在能们的去信上作了批示。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"aaa1b91015"}],"page":{"id":"924cf2aaed","publicationId":"maoquanji13","articleId":"aaa1b91015","start":523,"end":523}}}},"__N_SSG":true}